Interface TableCellRenderer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTableCellRenderer, DefaultTableCellRenderer, EntityListTableCellRenderer

    public interface TableCellRenderer

    An interface used to create components which display data in a cell of a Table.

        Component getTableCellRendererComponent(Table table,
                                        Object value,
                                        boolean isSelected,
                                        boolean hasFocus,
                                        int row,
                                        int column)

        Create a component to display the content of a particular cell of the table.

        Parameters:
        table - The table.
        value - The cell value to display.
        isSelected - Whether the cell is currently selected.
        hasFocus - Whether the cell currently has focus.
        row - The row number (0-based).
        column - The column number (0-based)
        Returns:
        The component to display the content.
